{"tid":2036107,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"犯法就係犯法，除非 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2020-05-26T09:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T10:03:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"96e9d63e6df2254bc05d20d7550210055f6c6f2e","tid":2036107,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:20:18.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20200526/20924533/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200526%2F20924533%2F&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA3%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=c91c046a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200526%2F20924533%2F&h=c0315b1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20200526/20924533/</a><br />\n<br />\n犯法就係犯法，除非 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200526/large/1590390468_f9fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200526%2Flarge%2F1590390468_f9fd.jpg&h=6ae93a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人有很多相認的暗號，街頭喊一句「董建華」，街尾便會有人高呼「下臺」。這邊喊一句「民&times;聯」，那邊便回應一句「最無恥」。你喊「五大訴求」，那邊說「缺一不可」。你叫「香港人」，那邊喊「加油/報仇/反抗」。<br />\n<br />\n警察也是暗號來源大戶。基於警察係大晒，國安法就到，我不敢冒犯皇軍尊嚴，只出上聯，下聯大家都明白。<br />\n<br />\n上聯是「好仔唔當差」，下聯自己知。上聯是「香港警察」，下聯又是千變萬化。<br />\n<br />\n今天最新版本，便是「犯法就係犯法」，「除非你係警察」。<br />\n<br />\n不言自明，。。。。。。。。。。甚至有人發起到便利店查詢「警察買水後數優惠計劃」。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。對人民軍隊的要求是「三大紀律、八項注意」，三大紀律是「一切行動聽指揮；不拿群眾一針一線；一切繳獲要歸公。」<br />\n<br />\n用這個標準審視香港專業優秀的警察，發現難以完全符合。傳媒拍攝到有白衣指揮官和前線防暴有不同意見，指揮官嗌停但防暴照衝，不聽行動指揮。<br />\n<br />\n不拿群眾一針一線，卻拿了店鋪的水而不付款。如果事後付款也是付款，那麼世上應無高買，一切都是後數。至於一切繳獲要歸公，那宗警員掃毒後將毒品私自扣起的「販冰兵」案件，便沒有做到「歸公」的要求。所以不要再說香港警察是「大陸化」，實在是對大陸人民解放軍叔叔最大侮辱。<br />\n<br />\n八項注意包括「說話和氣；買賣公平；借東西要還；損壞東西要賠償；不打人罵人；不損壞莊稼；不調戲婦女；不虐待俘虜。」<br />\n<br />\nWell，單單第一句「說話和氣」已經KO，「上番行人路啊！開香檳啊我地今晚！&times;你！死曱甴&hellip;&hellip;」 <br />\n<br />\n曾志豪<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"3b87fc93f152d98edf89eddaf5aa2d8aeb32fa9e","tid":2036107,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"［突發］有人起ig搞左個「#全城㩒美元」挑戰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476098</a>"},{"pid":"1bc52c9e5a4d827f567dd282cb9c605d3309e8d2","tid":2036107,"uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:29:25.000Z","msg":"販冰兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1da13c895ab34c777b41320939b3f0ed52ff46e","tid":2036107,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對人民軍隊的要求是「三大紀律、八項注意」，三大紀律是「一切行動聽指揮；不拿群眾一針一線；一切繳獲要歸公。」</blockquote>佢當全世界係敵對, 咪唔洗守呢個規則"},{"pid":"ebbed46d6f95aca265317753972a9d727b8efff4","tid":2036107,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:57:29.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13f8bf80a75bff1a8e3e111425c8eab42fa3abf","tid":2036107,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:59:39.000Z","msg":"link 呢"},{"pid":"b7fa505dbd0dcc455704d34705b6dadffa894e3e","tid":2036107,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"以前共匪未揸fit，梗係會做啲門面嘢呃下民心<br />\n<br />\n而家呢班已經係極權嘅爪牙，連戲都費事做啦"}]}